text: Gyula Kakas was a gymnast from Hungary. Gyula competed at the 1896 Summer Olympics. He was born on 28 March 1875 and died on 25 February 1928.Gyula Kakas ==References== == Other websites == * Category:1875 births Category:1928 deaths Category:Hungarian gymnasts Category:Olympians for Hungary Category:Sportspeople from Budapest
